She felt a hand on her shoulder. She saw Carnitron. "It's about time. 
Help up blast some Maximals."  She heard his last comment and 
frowned. Sometimes, it was best not to fight your comrads while 
fighting the enimy at the same time. She shot at the maximals and 
felt her body start to recharge.
